name: Hooked on Tech
description: The Philippines is quite known for its internet usage, which earned it the title "The Social Media Capital of the World". Tech has become so ubiquitous that street kids are jacked into cyberspace with smartphones and wireless infrastructure. If blockchain tech becomes even more widespread, it would have endless applications especially in the Philippines and its tech-obsessed culture. My entry for #WorldArtDay2021 and #NFTsForAll under the theme of "Technology". By Lucius Felimus
